{"tid":764110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲玩棚改？城投公司已經有新版塊項目!","createTime":"2018-08-01T16:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T02:59:53.000Z","uid":182475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"168679855a75e11eb9dda30ac090d0117183bf98","tid":764110,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【強推火葬】江西禁村民入土為安 政府後面擁巨大利益</span><br />\n<br />\n江西省當局近日力推殯葬改革，強行收繳民眾的棺木，甚至起出新落葬的死者的棺木，強行火葬，引發全國不滿。內地媒體指，江西強力推動改革，<span style=\"color: red;\">原來是官方參股成立的公司</span>，要謀取殯葬背後的巨大利益。<br />\n<br />\n鳳凰網報道指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">一間名為「江西省殯葬投資集團」去年11月成立，註冊資金2億元人民幣，3大股東當中的「江西大成國有資產經營管理」，就是江西省國資委下的國有獨資公司。</span>這間公司成立不到1年，已經包攬江西豐城、樂平、新余等6地的殯葬項目，對現有的殯葬進行改革，及興建城市公墓、公益墓地。江西省國資委的資料，稱成立殯葬投資集團，是「國有資本佈局優化和市場化戰略重組成果」。<br />\n　<br />\n與此同時，一間辦公室設在江西省政府民政廳大樓的公司「江西南方環保」，則是主力生產火化機，產品在內地廣泛使用，包括北京八寶山殯儀館、澳門等地的火葬場，還聲稱遠銷俄羅斯、馬來西亞等國家。這間公司涉及一宗合同糾紛的訴訟文書顯示，2004年一部火化機的地方政府採購價為56萬元人民幣。​​​​分析指，當地實行100%火化，將會增加這公司的利潤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180801/58513078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F58513078&d=SwJpf8I4kQRkFR2dERQ81Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=42a2b177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F58513078&h=9b5fe019\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180801/58513078</a>"},{"pid":"69af3ce97cf13cf621c8d89a174c23657d1341ef","tid":764110,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"大發死人財"},{"pid":"304d9263791c37b0d7d6b1932fe729c3167f26ef","tid":764110,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e55bdb1b95fd5d1dbb336b6e90802d5c61fc4","tid":764110,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「國有資本佈局優化和市場化戰略重組成果」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac569d797b3c1dd258cceb42c657d8beb543164","tid":764110,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58896b148955dd74cb7c6c2eacadc16b38cca76","tid":764110,"uid":46900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:15:04.000Z","msg":"福壽園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc2e7396ca8455fe8a804f88f1c008fe00e693f","tid":764110,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:59:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫棚改？"}]}